#Product Backlog

* Player with white pieces starts
* Show allowed moves when clicking on a piece
* Automatically moves the Rook on castling
* Show captured pieces
* Display names of players
* Time control
* Refuse not allowed moves
* Undo
* Export game in algebraic notation
* Import and play game (interactive)
* Redo
* 3D display
* Network game
* ELO rating
* The same player cannot play twice in a row


#Build Instructions

With Buildr
1. install buildr : gem install buildr
2. see the tests  : buildr test
3. play           : buildr chess:run

With Ant
1. install ant    : http://ant.apache.org/
2. see the tests  : ant test
3. play           : ant play



